One of the bigger cold storage.
Selling huge selection of foodstuffs, there are the normal standard items found in normal supermarket, this store also sells, roasted meat as well (supposedly it was cooked in-house). There is also a sushi section too.
For this particular outlet, the organic section can be considered well-stocked up, there are the organic fresh produce and also the organic packed items.
One aspect I liked about this outlet, is there is a fresh nuts section. You can select the choice of nuts and bag them. Fast and easy.
This store was well maintained and was kept clean. You could constantly see the staffs, packing and arranging the items.
There are also the normal checkout counters and also the self service counters.
Good place to do your grocery shopping!
